        "content": "<p>I thought I recall one of the talks I've seen on Roc mentioned that Bool was just a tag union of [True, False]. But it seems now it's a special type with values <code>Bool.true</code> and <code>Bool.false</code>. Am I misremembering, or did that change?</p>",
